name: Dropspotting | Choose Life
description:
Choose life. Choose a blockchain. Choose a wallet. Choose a nickname. Choose a fucking pfp.  
Choose SuperRare, Foundation, Rarible, and OpenSea. 
Choose Twitter, Discord, and Telegram.  
Choose WGMI. Choose Web3. Choose DeFi. Choose DAO.  
Choose to mint. Choose to burn. Choose to bid.  
Choose your friends. Choose to say GM and wonder who the fuck you are every morning.  Choose to stare at that screen reading those mind-numbing tweets,  
Spirit-crushing talks about what's crypto art,  
Stuffing fucking junk .JPGs into your brain. 
Choose to rot away at the end of every single scroll,  
Pissing your last while you are lost in a miserable metaverse,   
A fantasyland for fucked-up brat avatars you have spawned to replace yourselves.  
Choose NFT. Choose your future. Choose life.
